<li>Newton, Michael, <i>The Encyclopedia of Unsolved Crimes</i>, Checkmark Books, 2004, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0816049815" class="internal">ISBN 0-8160-4981-5</a></li>
<li>Norris, William, "A Talent to Deceive", SynergEbooks,2007, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780744315943" class="internal">ISBN 978-0-7443-1594-3</a></li>
